<i>noun</i>: 환멸 [환ː멸] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>환멸 [환ː멸]</dt><br>
<dd>disillusion; disenchantment; letdown</dd><br>
<dd>꿈이나 기대가 깨어짐. 또는 그때 느끼는 괴로운 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one's dream or expectation falls to pieces; or a feeling of agony that one has in such a situation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>